        What to Expect When Selling in Upper Mount Gravatt
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Upper Mount Gravatt is an elevated southern suburb with strong retail access, good schools and a practical family buyer pool that values the Garden City precinct and the South East Freeway connection.
      </p>
    </div>
